      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>Shading and Look Development in Maya is natural using Maya's built in look development tools, combined with Pixar's powerful BXDFs. Using a combination of Pixar and Maya patterns with the multitude of available BXDFs, any look can be achieved.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540557/Lama_Stirling_top.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431558775&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=732\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540557/Lama_Stirling_top.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431558775&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1041\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540594\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Stirling_top.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540557\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"90e21613-108c-45a8-b832-2e9adf72ba8e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540557/Lama_Stirling_top.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431558775&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=1464 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544540557/Lama_Stirling_top.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431558775&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=732 1x\"></span><h3 id=\"ShadinginMaya-PatternNodes\">Pattern Nodes</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544539520/Supported+Maya+Nodes\" rel=\"nofollow\">Supported Native Maya Patterns</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544540645/Pixar+Patterns\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pixar Patterns</a> </p></li></ul><h3 id=\"ShadinginMaya-DisplacementNodes\">Displacement Nodes</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661545\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrDisplace</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661615\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrDispTransform</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661613\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrDispScalarLayer</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19662123\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrDispVectorLayer</a></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"ShadinginMaya-BXDFNodes\">BXDF Nodes</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544540950/PxrSurface+in+Maya\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrSurface</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544540989/Using+Material+Layers\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrLayeredSurface</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661553\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrMarschnerHair</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661555\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrVolume</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544541251/MaterialX+Lama+in+Maya\" rel=\"nofollow\">MaterialX Lama</a></p></li><li><p>PxrConstant - single color or texture</p></li><li><p>PxrBlack - does not scatter/reflect light</p></li></ul><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540557/Lama_Stirling_bottom.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431558774&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544540557/Lama_Stirling_bottom.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431558774&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"910\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544540591\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Stirling_bottom.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544540557\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1dcdcd9d-fc7a-4e0a-b31b-b66967ed16a9\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span>"
    }
